Package breakout.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Ball
    The Ball is a class that moves and destroys blocks.
    Block
    The Block class models a block that can be destroyed by Ball.
    Board
    The Board class aggregates block, ball, and paddle.
    Constants
    Holds all of the constants for the game.
    Leaderboard
    Keeps track of all scores and orders scores from highest to lowest.
    Life
    An object to keep track of lives.
    Paddle
    Moves left and right using keyboard arrows.
    Score
    Keeps track of the user's score.
